# type

**Instance Property**

The type value indicating how to interpret the payload.

## Declaration

```swift
var type: PKPushType { get }
```

## Discussion

For possible values, see [doc://com.apple.pushkit/documentation/PushKit/PKPushType].

## Payload Data

- **dictionaryPayload**: The contents of the received payload.
